README:

1.) Copy all maillearn-c.* files to a location that can not be accessed remotely.
2.) Install https://github.com/yahesh/pushinfo/
3.) Install https://github.com/yahesh/unchroot/
4.) Configure maillean-c.conf.phs and make sure that all paths are accessible.
5.) Configure CRON to call maillearn-c.phs regularly:
    0 0 * * * root php /path/to/maillearn-c.phs >/dev/null 2>&1
